node.text: NO, LEBRON!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 28, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, beard, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Ran for an hour on the treadmill this morning at 7.0 mph. 27 holes of golf this afternoon. Now I’m in the resort gym for my never-miss Mon/Wed/Fri weight session. Ernestine calls it Vacation Boot Camp and says we’ll need a vacation after our vacation. Nope: My endless vacation is dominating Shannon every single morning on Undisputed. #NoMercy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 28, 2021. May be an image of nature, tree and golf course.

node.text: Just finished playing 27 holes in the desert heat. Palm Springs is my paradise. Only 105 today. Cold front. #StayHydrated

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 28, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, Maltese and outdoors.

node.text: HAPPY ANNIVERSARY, ERNESTINE. Here are my two girls yesterday, Ernestine and Hazel. Ernestine won’t love me posting because she’s without makeup. She still looks pretty great to me. I love you, Ernestine.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 26, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Ahhhh, golf in Palm Springs. Give me 110 degrees and an empty course and I’m a a happy guy.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 23, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, wrist watch, footwear and indoor.

node.text: I can’t lose in these shoes. MJ FOREVER. #DripBayless

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 23, 2021.

node.text: I am up, prepping to steamroll Shannon on today’s Undisputed. I can sleep when I’m dead.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 17, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and Maltese.

node.text: Hazel and I, Saturday afternoon in LA, between the British Open and Game 5. Hazel says Suns big tonight.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 16, 2021.

node.text: Pretty cool way to leave the Fox Lot after Friday’s Undisputed … seeing through my car window a Skip & Shannon billboard featured out front. Thanks for making Undisputed the hottest sports show on television

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Skip Bayless on July 16, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and indoor.
